@d54 8
a61 10
PF is enabled by default.
If you wish to disable it on boot, add the line
<blockquote>
<tt>
pf=NO
</tt>
</blockquote>
to the file
<a href="http://www.openbsd.org/cgi-bin/man.cgi?query=rc.conf.local&amp;sektion=8"
>/etc/rc.conf.local</a> and reboot your system to have it take effect.
